      <title>本田在华裁员，三家工厂停产</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-11/honda-cuts-jobs-in-china-suspends-production-at-three-plants</link>
      <description><![CDATA[本田汽车公司正在削减工作岗位并暂停其在中国的三家工厂的生产，以寻求削减库存并致力于在全球最大汽车市场进行更广泛的战略转变。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-11/honda-cuts-jobs-in-china-suspends-production-at-three-plants</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Sep 2024 04:01:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
