      <title>中国债券干预导致短期利率下降、交易量增加</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-11/china-s-bond-intervention-sinks-short-end-rates-boosts-trading</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国对国内政府债券市场的干预导致各类市场出现异常，从非基准“特殊”证券交易激增到短期债券收益率下降。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-11/china-s-bond-intervention-sinks-short-end-rates-boosts-trading</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Sep 2024 04:00:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>油价跌至每桶60美元，为全球经济软着陆铺平道路</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-11/oil-s-fall-into-60s-widens-runway-for-the-global-economy-to-make-a-soft-landing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[如果一些对石油最为悲观的预测能够成真，那么世界发达经济体或许就有新的理由期待明年经济增长基础更加稳固。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-11/oil-s-fall-into-60s-widens-runway-for-the-global-economy-to-make-a-soft-landing</guid>
